{"title": "Bigotry Exception", "content": "A character who is well-liked or respected by bigoted individuals or institutions despite belonging to whatever group that's being discriminated against. Perhaps they had a friendship that predated whatever turned the bigots into bigots, perhaps there was a Fire Forged Friendship, perhaps they make the top guy laugh and no one crosses the top guy, perhaps they are so good they are worth making an exception for, perhaps they're just Token Minority cases for the others to point to as evidence that they're not really bigots at all. Whatever the case, it's obvious they are an exception.\n\nCompare and contrast You Are a Credit to Your Race and Some of My Best Friends Are X, the former generally being an attempt at a well-meaning statement just layered with plenty of unfortunate subtext, while the latter involves the trope invoker being in denial about their bigotry.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigotryException", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Manga/KaguyaSamaLoveIsWar", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/Viz", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/WhoFramedRogerRabbit", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/BettyBoop", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheThrawnTrilogy", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/HarryPotter", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/JRRTolkien", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheLordOfTheRings", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheLordOfTheRings", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheTwilightZone1959", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Theatre/MarginForError", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Theatre/FiddlerOnTheRoof", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheBoondocks", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/Futurama", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/StarVsTheForcesOfEvil", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/TheMagicBookOfSpells"], "non_media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FireForgedFriends", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TokenMinority", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/YouAreACreditToYourRace", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SomeOfMyBestFriendsAreX", "/pmwiki/pmwiki